  Chong2-si7 tui3 goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 si2 liau2-au7, goan2 chhu3-nih hit-pun2 Seng3-keng soa3 bo5 khi3. Kiam2-chhai2 si7 hou7 sin5-hu7 theh8 khi3. TaN chit-pun2 Seng3-keng piN3-choe3 chit-e5 kou3-su7 it-chhe3 e5 kun-goan5. Chit-pun2 Seng3-keng ia7 si7 ti7 goa2 siau3-lian5 e5 si5, chio3 jip8 goa2 e5 leng5-hun5 e5 kng, kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, hit-e5 kng boe7-bat hoa-khi3. Hit e5 kng iau2-ku2 ti7-teh. Tit8 kau3 kin-na2-jit8, hit-pun2 kho2-ai3 e5 Seng3-keng eng7 Siong7-te3 e5 chu5-ai3, hou7 goa2 seng5-siu7 bo5-hoat-tou7 thang heng5-iong5 e5 khoai3-lok8, goa2 kam2-kak i2-keng tit-tioh8 kiu3-siok8, ti7 hit tiong-kan tit-tioh8 kng chio3, ji7-chhiaN2 oe7 thang ti7 chin-li2 e5 chheng-choaN5 lai5 lim-chiah8. 
  Chong2-si7 kiam2-chhai2 li2 beh tui3 goa2 an2-ni mng7: ¡§Thian-chu2-kau3 e5 sin5-hu7 kiam2 m7-si7 m7 chun2 in e5 kau3-iu2 thak8 Seng3-keng mah?¡¨ Si7, pun2-lai5 si7 an2-ni. Chong2-si7 kam2-sia7 Chu2, kin-na2-jit8 e5 su7-sit8, chha-put-to choan5 se3-kai3 e5 Thian-chu2-kau3 long2 seng5-jin7 un2-chun2 lang5 thak8 Seng3-keng, ia7 ti7 chit8-koa2 sin3 Thian-chu2-kau3 e5 ka-teng5 tiong, li2 oe7 thang hoat-hian7 in u7 Seng3-keng. 
