  Chong2-si7 kam2-sia7 su3-hok e5 Siong7-te3, goa2 mui2-pai2 thak8 Seng3-keng e5 si5, u7 chit8-chiong2 sin5-pi3 e5 siaN tui3 goa2 kong2, ¡§Li2 kiam2 bo5 khoaN3-chhut ti7 Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2 kau3-hoe7, lin2 bo5 sun7-than3 Siong7-te3 sou2 ka3-si7 e5 oe7, chi2-u7 sun7-than3 lang5 e5 thoan5-thong2?¡¨ Ti7 am3-si5 chheng-cheng7 e5 si5, goa2 thiaN tioh8 hit e5 siaN-im chiu7 thi5-khau3 lau5 bak8-sai2, chong2-si7 hit-e5 siaN iu5-goan5 chhin-chhiuN7 lui5 e5 siaN teh hoan2-hok. Goa2 ai3 tiam3 ti7 Seng3 Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2 kau3-hoe7 lai5 oah8, lai5 si2, sou2-i2 goa2 chiu7 ki5-to2 kiu5 Siong7-te3 hou7 chit-e5 siaN tiam7-khi3, chong2-si7 goa2 thiaN-kiN3 hit-e5 siaN-im iu5-goan5 na2 toa7-soaN. Tng goa2 thak8 I e5 Oe7 e5 si5, I siuN7 beh thau2-khui goa2 e5 so2-lian7, chong2-si7 goa2 bo5 ai3 goa2 e5 so2-lian7 siu7 thau2-khui. I toa3 I chin2-kiu3 e5 kng lai5 chiu7-kun7 goa2, chong2-si7 goa2 bo5 beh chiap-lap8 I. 
